---
import site from '@/lib/site';
---

<section class="section s3-benefits">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="s3-benefits__intro">
      <h2 class="s3-benefits__heading">Why NAD+ Injection Is the Smart Choice for Busy Lifestyles</h2>
      <p class="s3-benefits__body">Get the cellular benefits of NAD+ therapy in a fraction of the time. Perfect for those who want results without a lengthy appointment.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="s3-benefits__grid">

      <div class="s3-benefits__card">
        <h3 class="s3-benefits__card-title">Quick &amp; Convenient</h3>
        <p class="s3-benefits__card-body">Your NAD+ Injection takes just a few minutes. Walk in, get your shot, and get back to your day feeling recharged. Ideal for busy professionals and parents in Millburn and Short Hills.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s3-benefits__card">
        <h3 class="s3-benefits__card-title">Sharper Mental Clarity &amp; Focus</h3>
        <p class="s3-benefits__card-body">Brain fog holding you back? NAD+ supports healthy brain function and helps you think clearer, focus longer, and stay sharp throughout your day.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s3-benefits__card">
        <h3 class="s3-benefits__card-title">Natural Energy Without the Crash</h3>
        <p class="s3-benefits__card-body">NAD+ works at the cellular level to support your body's natural energy production. No jitters, no caffeine crash. Just steady, clean energy that lasts.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s3-benefits__card">
        <h3 class="s3-benefits__card-title">Anti-Aging From the Inside Out</h3>
        <p class="s3-benefits__card-body">NAD+ levels drop as we age. Replenishing them helps support cellular repair, healthy metabolism, and overall vitality. You'll feel younger, longer.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="s3-benefits__cta">
      <a
        href={site.calcomUrl}
        class="btn btn--primary btn--lg"
      >
        Schedule Your NAD+ Injection Today
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .s3-benefits__intro {
    max-width: var(--container-narrow);
    margin-inline: auto;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .s3-benefits__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s3-benefits__body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .s3-benefits__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .s3-benefits__card {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.05);
  }

  .s3-benefits__card-title {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--weight-bold);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s3-benefits__card-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .s3-benefits__cta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .s3-benefits__grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .s3-benefits__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .s3-benefits__cta .btn {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
